Help Center

Frequently Asked Questions

Do you offer Cash on Delivery (COD)?

Yes! We offer COD on all orders across India. No prepayment required — simply pay when your package arrives at your doorstep.

How long does delivery take?

Standard delivery takes 5–7 working days across India. For metro cities like Delhi, Mumbai, Bangalore — it may arrive sooner in 3–4 days.

Is shipping free?

Yes! Shipping is completely free on all orders above ₹999. For orders below ₹999, a nominal shipping fee of ₹49 is charged.

What is your return policy?

We offer a 7-day return policy from the date of delivery. If you receive a damaged or wrong product, contact us on WhatsApp within 7 days and we'll arrange a pickup and full refund.

How do I track my order?

Once your order is shipped, you will receive a tracking ID via WhatsApp or email. You can use that to track your order on the courier partner's website.

Are your products authentic and good quality?

Absolutely. Every product on Aesthetic Buys is carefully handpicked and quality-checked before listing. We stand behind everything we sell.

How can I place an order via WhatsApp?

Simply click "WhatsApp Us" anywhere on the site, tell us the product name and your delivery address, and we'll process your order instantly. It's that simple!

Can I cancel my order?

Orders can be cancelled within 12 hours of placing them. After that, the order may already be dispatched. Contact us immediately on WhatsApp for cancellation requests.
